data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-story residence that boats 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a plethora of updates to enhance your living experience. Enjoy the convenience of first-floor laundry, master walk in closet and bask in the natural light streaming through the sun window in the living room. Step inside to discover a fresh ambiance, with fresh paint throughout completed in 2023. Makeover in 2021, featuring new carpeting upstairs, updated lighting in the living room, dining room, and porch, as well as almost all new windows. Updated bathroom, completed in 2018, and appreciate the recent plumbing upgrades in the upstairs bathroom and the addition of a new toilet downstairs. This home offers a blend of functionality and style. Outside the landscaping have been meticulously redone, ensuring a welcoming exterior to greet you everyday. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully updated home yours! Listing agent is related to seller.
